Justice, Drug </p>

<p> Enforcement Administration, 1990. </p>

<p> 3. Laszlo, A.T. &quot;Clandestine Drug Laboratories:
Confronting a Growing </p>

<p> National Crisis.&quot; National Sheriff, 41 (1989): 9-14. </p>

