<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<p>A Criminal Justice System Strategy for Treating Cocaine-Heroin
Abusing Offenders in Custody </p>

<p> <b>National Institute of Justice</b> </p>

<p> <b>James K. Stewart, Director.</b> </p>

