<h1>Federal Convictions of Public Officials </h1>

<p> <b>1970 - 1988</b> </p>

<p> <b>Excerpted from THE ECONOMICS OF PROHIBITION, </b> </p>

<p> <b>by Mark Thornton. </b> </p>

<p> <b>Reference Source: USDoJ &quot;Report to Congress on the
Activities and Operations of the Public Integrity Section&quot; </b>
</p>

<p> <img src="../graphics/blueline.gif" align="BOTTOM"> </p>

